!! Black background: 32 bit (24 bits + 8 for alpha), partially transparent
!urxvt*background:         rgba:0000/0000/0000/7fff
!urxvt*depth:              32
!! Pseudo-transparent
urxvt*background:         black
URxvt*transparent:        true
